The evidence with the title 'The rich, the poor and the growing gap between them | the Economist ' says Jun 15, 2006  ... The gap between rich and poor is bigger than in any other advanced country , but most people are unconcerned .  ... In the late 1990s everybody shared in this boom .  ... Despite a quarter century during which incomes have drifted ever farther apart , the distribution of wealth has remained remarkably stable . 
